<item>
<title>朋友的博文：速递（2）</title>
<link></link>
<pubDate>Thu, 08 Jan 2009 23:44:30 +0000</pubDate>
<dc:creator>yourusername</dc:creator>

		<category><![CDATA[]]></category>

<guid isPermaLink="false"></guid>
<description></description>
<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>
<div>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial">朋友的博文，定期清理，分门别类张贴之：</font> <br /></div>
<div> </div>
<div><b><font size="2" face="Arial">聚会</font></b></div>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial">小齐，&quot;<a href="http://achyia.spaces.live.com/Blog/cns!610DF96F0C047906!2828.entry" target="_blank">小妇人</a>&quot;</font></div>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial">萍踪，&quot;<a href="http://baitahe.spaces.live.com/Blog/cns!155879A0696B9286!557.entry" target="_blank">张府行</a>&quot;</font></div>
<div> </div>
<div><b><font size="2" face="Arial">生活</font></b></div>
<div> </div>
