<a href="http://panshanghu.spaces.live.com/" target="_blank">http://panshanghu.spaces.live.com/</a><br />技术博客（数据挖掘、金融计算、SAS、etc.）: <a href="http://johnthu.spaces.live.com/" target="_blank">http://johnthu.spaces.live.com/</a>
</font></p></div>
]]></content:encoded>
